Jean Angelo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Angelo 0 Jean Angelo (17 May 1888 - 26 November 1933) born Jean-Jacques Barthélémy was a French film actor of silent movies and early talkies. He was often a leading man playing romantic or athletic roles. Angelo was born and died in Paris.
